name: Mask Nesting Side Tables
description: The Mask Nesting Side Tables by Kifu Paris are versatile and organic pieces. The amorphous tops and bases are inlaid in a mixture of shagreen, shell or quartz with bronze-patina brass. This piece is designed by Kifu Augousti the daughter of Ria and Yiouri Augousti. Available in other finishes. Can be purchased separately, see other listings.
